This paper deals with the analysis of spatially embedded contact networks, which involves the study of both network structure and spatial structure. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Spatial Data Analysis (cs.SD), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE), and Sociology (cs.SOC).
